{"tid":610020,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍緊拖既你地覺得熱戀期有幾耐","createTime":"2018-03-29T13:58:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T14:24:53.000Z","uid":43062,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d766c5752b229d06100740fa2628b70473c9ffff","tid":610020,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T13:58:35.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  純粹想知下有拍拖既會有幾耐仲keep係熱戀期，有人話三個月，有人話半年，有人甚至兩年，你地又經歷左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n熱戀之後你地又係點樣保持住大家愛既感覺呢？間中既驚喜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊分享下熱戀幸福事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋磚先：夜晚十一點幾另一半突然係樓下出現，買左碗糖水陪我一齊食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9102487b00770766ad311feef54cbee3c25a1b9b","tid":610020,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好，我同女朋友熱戀期好似已經過左，同佢兩年幾左右<br />\n<br />\n主要係因為溝通成日唔夾，同成日嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb872d40efae6ea0f0960d63374c1b6cd5a5622d","tid":610020,"uid":43062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9102487b00770766ad311feef54cbee3c25a1b9b","tid":610020,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"樓主真係好，我同女朋友熱戀期好似已經過左，同佢兩年幾左右<br />\n<br />\n主要係因為溝通成日唔夾，同成日嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T17:42:07.000Z","msg":"嗌交都起碼叫有交流，最難搞係冷暴力，嘈都冇聲，一切玩內心戲最大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edb578d95e69f10639f9c20e8c53642ee0c3fde","tid":610020,"uid":67315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T19:43:20.000Z","msg":"幾日？一個月？<br />\n其實唔太識分係咪熱戀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">又或者呢年幾兩年一直係掛</span></span>"},{"pid":"037cf04999df892ff3313b76608a2d97f02f2ea8","tid":610020,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"之前以為半年一年就熱戀完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但而家年幾都仲好sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805d4b37a9f564fe4b464b1e8e351b3be4b4fe39","tid":610020,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"雖然我地成撚日鬧交<br />\n但我覺得差唔多一年都仲熱戀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2766f0053771f98efecf3aeb88171b5eff672eb1","tid":610020,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"805d4b37a9f564fe4b464b1e8e351b3be4b4fe39","tid":610020,"uid":2263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T02:27:34.000Z","msg":"雖然我地成撚日鬧交<br />\n但我覺得差唔多一年都仲熱戀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"你個名就知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f4129269eb1538bf3ded5316369d0c4caf9b5e","tid":610020,"uid":2220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T04:25:21.000Z","msg":"年幾 仲熱緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa442ffde6e71870284b132205330650c661452","tid":610020,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T04:28:32.000Z","msg":"仲熱戀緊既巴絲有冇咩心得分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  求教學"},{"pid":"c9f740154bd84c3d666f7cfb9413daec913f0c7a","tid":610020,"uid":111625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941bad920dbbe3f738f8e68934f3fb8d1699388a","tid":610020,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"如果大家識得欣賞對方嘅好<br />\n就日日都係熱戀期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8497f4209ddb5a25ed3575acc3b0def6635ade84","tid":610020,"uid":36758,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"我覺得要識得互相欣賞，互相體諒<br />\n唔需要經常甜言密語<br />\n但得閒可以真誠咁讚下對方<br />\n俾對方知道佢嘅重要性<br />\n<br />\n我同另一伴係first love<br />\n就黎踏入第十一年<br />\n唔係成日見面傾電話<br />\n但都仲覺得係幸福地熱戀中<br />\n熱戀期無話幾耐<br />\n係睇大家點維繫<br />\n加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a894b8b818044167019f372a7bb7c0d9335997c9","tid":610020,"uid":179758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T13:22:21.000Z","msg":"性格問題，雙方互相遷就，日日都係熱戀期。<br />\n單方面付出，好快挽完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7e397501848afb55a0f11323f4218290386297","tid":610020,"uid":45206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"兩三個月呱"},{"pid":"d3903df22e5cd9b35645184cc82548b4849445b5","tid":610020,"uid":124545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:24:53.000Z","msg":"我同另一半都係好脾氣 從來都唔鬧交<br />\n我平時會煮飯比佢氹佢開心<br />\n佢又成日突發等我收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經三年但每日都仲熱戀咁<br />\n每日都會抽時間見對方<br />\n佢既金句係<br />\n我無約你果日 我就會等你收工<br />\n我約左你果日 就係會同你去街<br />\n平凡是福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}